<div>
  <div>
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="form-description">
        <h3>Save a reference to your character for easy access</h3>
        <p>
          The following shortcuts are enabled on <img class="inline-image" src="/modules/vtta-dndbeyond/img/ddb-icon.png"> button the if you are setting the URL to your charactersheet below:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>SHIFT + Left-Click:</b >Opens the D&amp;D Beyond character sheet in a new window</li>
          <li><b>ALT + Left-Click:</b> Opens the JSON of your character in a new window</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          The URL should look like this:
          <b>https://www.dndbeyond.com/profile/<i>[Username]</i>>/characters/<i>[CharacterID]</i></b>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="form-caption">
        URL
        <span class="dndbeyond-url-status"
          >{{#if actor.data.flags.vtta.dndbeyond.url}}<i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: green"></i>{{else}}<i></i>{{/if}}</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="form-content">
        <input
          type="text"
          name="dndbeyond-url"
          value="{{#if actor.data.flags.vtta.dndbeyond.url}}{{actor.data.flags.vtta.dndbeyond.url}}{{/if}}"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div><hr></div>
    <div class="form-section">
      <div class="form-description">
        <h3>Import your character</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Open your character's sheet in D&amp;D Beyond</li>
          <li>Add <b>/json</b> to the URL in the address bar of your browser, then press <strong>Enter</strong></li>
          <li>
            <strong>Be patient!</strong> Wait for the whole page to load. This can take a couple of seconds, wait for
            the spinning loading icon to stop.
          </li>
          <li><b>On Chrome</b> press CTRL-A to select everything and then CTRL-C to copy it into the clipboard</li>
          <li><b>On Firefox</b> press the Button "Copy" to copy the contents into the clipboard</li>
          <li>Select the textarea below and paste the data with CTRL-V</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="form-caption">JSON</div>
      <div class="form-content"><textarea id="json"></textarea></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div></div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="task-name">Status</h2>
  </div>
</div>
